data.description: If you are looking for one level - open concept living in West Knoxville, this is the home for you. This beautiful home home in Campbell Station Villas features hardwood floors in main living area, luxurious kitchen with granite counters, breakfast bar/ island and large pantry with glamorous door. It has 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths for maximum convenience and privacy. Master has double trey ceiling, French doors lead to master bath with double vanity; walk in shower and large walk in closet. Outback you will find screened in porch and backyard with wrought iron fence. Additionally there is large storage area above the garage.Proximity is perfect - 5 minutes to I-40 - Turkey Creek and West Knox amenities. Come check out this beautiful home.
